The paper deals with the issue of ad-blockers and ad-block detection on the web, which falls under the category of web security and privacy (cs.CR). The authors also use machine learning techniques to automatically detect ad-block detection, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper discusses the different strategies used by websites for ad-block detection, which could fall under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI).
